'''Johnny Yau Chung Ling''' (邱仲凌) is a [[Hong Kong]] [[businessman]], the Managing Director of a [[China|Chinese]] based [[mass media]] [[company]] named [[Media Plus Hong Kong Limited]] in Hong Kong, [[China]]. Yau has been working for at least 35 years in TV production, [[advertising]], sales, [[marketing]] planning and [[international]] [[business]] [[developments]], and acquiring businesses both in Hong Kong and other overseas TV media. He worked at [[TVB]] and [[TVBI]] for more than 25 years and was the General Manager of [[Television Broadcast Satellite Limited]].

In addition, Yau has career achievements including launching [[Television Channel|TV channels]] in [[Singapore]], [[Malaysia]], [[Japan]], [[Australia]] and [[China]]. These channels include [[Astro (television)|Astro]] Wah LaiToh, [[TVBS-Asia]], [[TVBJ]], [[TVB8]] and Xing He Channel (星河頻道). He was also the General Manager of Azio International TV (吉本東風) and Director of Content Land Inc. Ltd..

