'''Yuri Vadimovich Korablin''' ({{lang-ru|link=no|Юрий Вадимович Кораблин}}; 30 January 1960 – 20 September 2016) was a Russian businessman, investor, and politician, born in [[Moscow]]. Former mayor of [[Khimki]], Korablin became owner of Italian football club [[F.B.C. Unione Venezia|Unione Venezia]] in February 2011.<ref>[http://www.blitzquotidiano.it/sport/venezia-patron-russo-yuri-korablin-770079/ Venezia calcio: ecco il nuovo patron russo Yuri Korablin, obiettivo il ritorno in serie A]</ref><ref>[http://corrieredelveneto.corriere.it/veneto/notizie/cronaca/2016/20-settembre-2016/venezia-addio-yuri-korablin-240915653252.shtml Venezia, addio a Yuri Korablin]</ref>
